content.rendered:
On November 2, representatives of Intellectsoft’s Norwegian office will be attending the “Technology. Marketing. Leadership.” conference which is organized by Oslo Business Forum. The event will be held in Colosseum Kino — the largest cinema hall in Northern Europe.

Oslo Business Forum once again gathers the top executives in Norwegian business in one place to network and listen to business leaders from the world’s most prominent companies.

On this event, the attendees will have a chance to hear a lecture from the digital marketing mastermind and New York Times best-selling author Gary Vaynerchuk.

The rest of the panel includes Anita Krohn Traaseth, Administrative Director of Innovation Norway; Jan Grønbech, CEO of Google Norway; Sven Thaulow, Administrative Director of Cisco Norway; and Thomas Anglero, Innovation Director of IBM.

The attendees will have an opportunity to network between lectures.

If you’re attending the conference, let’s schedule a meeting beforehand — so we can have a productive discussion about your software project.

excerpt.rendered: Intellectsoft will attend the biggest business event of the season in North Europe.
